Kirkpatrick's Four-Level Training Evaluation Model
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Apply Kirkpatrick's four-level evaluation model to assess training effectiveness
Develop Python scripts to analyze training data across all four levels
Create evaluation metrics for reaction, learning, behavior, and results
Generate data visualizations for training evaluation insights
Calculate ROI and business impact of training programs
